69
00:08:45,641 --> 00:08:48,166
Well, sure you have. I've had some myself.

70
00:08:48,344 --> 00:08:50,244
Yes, I know.

71
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:53,048
Listen, baby, we're a team.

72
00:08:53,216 --> 00:08:55,184
We're playing the big time.
See that?

73
00:08:55,351 --> 00:08:58,081
Nadine & Hewes?
That's written in stardust.

74
00:08:58,254 --> 00:09:00,313
They've offered me
a wonderful contract.

75
00:09:00,489 --> 00:09:02,286
They say they'll star me.

76
00:09:02,458 --> 00:09:04,824
And you can dance with anyone.

77
00:09:05,161 --> 00:09:07,095
Well, wait a minute.

78
00:09:08,164 --> 00:09:09,825
I suppose I could.

79
00:09:09,999 --> 00:09:11,830
I've danced with lots of girls.

80
00:09:12,001 --> 00:09:14,765
It's always been just a business.

81
00:09:15,071 --> 00:09:17,335
That was before I met you.

82
00:09:20,343 --> 00:09:23,141
This isn't just dancing. It's...

83
00:09:23,446 --> 00:09:25,641
It's different.

84
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:28,579
This is...

85
00:09:28,818 --> 00:09:30,410
...us.

86
00:09:30,753 --> 00:09:36,692
<i>It only happens</i>
<i>When I dance with you</i>

87
00:09:38,261 --> 00:09:44,598
<i>That trip to heaven</i>
<i>Till the dance is through</i>

88
00:09:45,935 --> 00:09:51,601
<i>With no one else do the heavens</i>
<i>Seem quite so near</i>

89
00:09:52,008 --> 00:09:55,341
<i>Why does it happen, dear</i>

90
00:09:55,778 --> 00:09:59,544
<i>Only with you?</i>

91
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:07,749
<i>Two cheeks together</i>
<i>Can be so divine</i>

92
00:10:08,891 --> 00:10:15,660
<i>But only when those cheeks</i>
<i>Are yours and mine</i>

93
00:10:16,465 --> 00:10:23,462
<i>I've danced with dozens of others</i>
<i>The whole night through</i>

94
00:10:24,006 --> 00:10:27,237
<i>But the thrill that comes with spring</i>

95
00:10:27,410 --> 00:10:31,176
<i>When anything could happen</i>

96
00:10:32,014 --> 00:10:36,951
<i>That only happens with you</i>

97
00:11:33,309 --> 00:11:36,437
<i>But the thrill that comes with spring</i>

98
